Xinhua News Agency Nanchang, May 22 (Reporter Chen Yushan): Recently, reporters learned from the Jiangxi Provincial Education Department that in order to enhance the guarantee of the shortage of subject teachers and achieve the balanced development of rural compulsory education, since 2016, Jiangxi Province has planned to use three years to train 10,000 qualified music, art, and physical education teachers for each rural (township and below) primary school in the province.
